des:
HBN Smart products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your outlets.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your outlets - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your outlets products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "HBN Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "HBN Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some HBN Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "HBN Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "HBN Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "HBN Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "HBN Smart", and you'll be navigated to "HBN Smart" login page;
(9). Enter the account and password of "HBN Smart" App；
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the outlet.”
“Alexa, turn off the outlet.”
